    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like a dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or dent anywhere. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a quick sale to help with some upcoming plans. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
