    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. Mechanically flawless, the crucial 'Big Three' have been addressed: rod bearings replaced with VAC coated shells, a comprehensive Beisan Systems Vanos overhaul, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain is paired with a crisp 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. Suspension has been subtly enhanced with Bilstein PSS10 coilovers for improved damping without compromising street compliance. Zero oil leaks, no VANOS rattle, and a pristine undercarriage. This is a turnkey, high-performance machine for the discerning purist.",
